WEBVTT

00:00:15.661 --> 00:00:23.043 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Look around us now;
See the love on each face—

00:00:23.043 --> 00:00:29.049 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Out there in the world,
hard to find.

00:00:29.049 --> 00:00:36.640 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
All these faithful friends
With the love they all show,

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:42.563 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Glad to leave
that old world behind.

00:00:42.563 --> 00:00:57.119 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love never fails; that’s promised.
It always will endure.

00:00:57.119 --> 00:01:07.171 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love—unfailing love—
That’s what Jehovah gives.

00:01:07.171 --> 00:01:10.883 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That’s what he is.

00:01:10.883 --> 00:01:20.893 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love—unfailing love—
That’s what we need to live.

00:01:20.893 --> 00:01:32.071 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And the love here today,
In our heart may it stay—

00:01:32.071 --> 00:01:35.783 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Unfailing love.

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:46.710 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Though sometimes it seems
Like the cares of this life

00:01:46.710 --> 00:01:56.845 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Weigh us down and feel hard to bear,
Giving brings us joy

00:01:56.845 --> 00:02:06.689 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When we share faith and hope,
Comforted by God’s loving care.

